---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro"
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro"
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service — Tidy App" description="Terms of Service for Tidy ADHD Cleaning App">
  <Nav />
  <main class="pt-24 pb-16 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-stone-500 mb-10">Last updated: February 17, 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            By downloading or using Tidy ("the App"), you agree to these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use the App.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Use of the App</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">You agree to use Tidy only for lawful purposes. You may not:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-stone-600 text-sm list-disc list-inside">
            <li>Use the App in any way that violates applicable laws or regulations</li>
            <li>Attempt to reverse engineer, decompile, or modify the App</li>
            <li>Use the App to transmit harmful, offensive, or illegal content</li>
            <li>Share your account credentials with others</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Subscriptions and Billing</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-stone-600">
            <p class="leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-stone-900">Free Tier:</strong> Available without payment. Includes 2 rooms and basic task features.</p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-stone-900">Plus ($4.99/month):</strong> Subscription billed monthly. Includes unlimited rooms and all features.</p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-stone-900">Family ($7.99/month):</strong> Subscription billed monthly. Includes all Plus features plus up to 6 household members.</p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">Subscriptions auto-renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the renewal date. Manage or cancel subscriptions through your Google Play or Apple App Store account settings.</p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">Refunds are handled per Google Play and Apple App Store policies.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            All content, features, and functionality of the App — including but not limited to text, graphics, logos, and software — are owned by Tidy and protected by applicable intellectual property laws. You are granted a limited, non-exclusive license to use the App for personal, non-commercial purposes.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Your Content</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            You retain ownership of all data you create within the App (tasks, rooms, schedules). By using the App, you grant us a limited license to store and process this data solely to provide the App's services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            Tidy is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, express or implied. We do not warrant that the App will be error-free or uninterrupted.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            To the maximum extent permitted by law, Tidy shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of the App.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            We may update these Terms at any time. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated Terms. We will notify users of significant changes via the App or email.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@tidyapp.me" class="text-primary-600 underline">legal@tidyapp.me</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
